clinton is the county seat of dewitt county and is located in the heart of central  at the intersection of state routes 51, 54 & 10, 161 miles southwest of chicago, 142 miles northeast of st. louis, and 45 miles northeast of springfield, the state capital, 45 miles from west of champaign-urbana, 22 miles south of bloomington/normal, and 18 miles north of decatur, which provides a great location for business, commercial and industrial interests.